QUERY_TEXT: WITH f2 AS (SELECT d1.dim1_pk, SUM(sales) AS agg_sales                 FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table2 f,                      nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1                 WHERE                       f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk                 GROUP BY d1.dim1_pk) SELECT d1.dim1_col4, SUM(f.orders), SUM(f2.agg_sales) FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table1 f      LEFT JOIN f2 ON (f.dim1_pk = f2.dim1_pk)       JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1 ON (f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk) GROUP BY d1.dim1_col4;

SELECT d1.dim1_col4, SUM(f.orders), SUM(f2.agg_sales) FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table1 f      LEFT JOIN       (      SELECT d1.dim1_pk, SUM(sales) AS agg_sales                 FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table2 f,                      nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1                 WHERE                       f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk                 GROUP BY d1.dim1_pk       ) f2        ON (f.dim1_pk = f2.dim1_pk)       JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1 ON (f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk) GROUP BY d1.dim1_col4;

SELECT d1.dim1_col4, SUM(f.orders), SUM(f2.agg_sales) FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table1 f      LEFT JOIN nz_rule_test.v_agg_sales f2 ON (f.dim1_pk = f2.dim1_pk)       JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1 ON (f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk) GROUP BY d1.dim1_col4;

SELECT d1.dim1_col3, d2.dim2_col3, SUM(sales), COUNT(orders) FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table1 f,      nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1,      nz_rule_test.dimension2 d2 WHERE         f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk      AND f.dim2_pk = d2.dim2_pk      AND      d1.dim1_col4 = 'Account_X0102' GROUP BY d1.dim1_col3, d2.dim2_col3 ORDER BY d2.dim2_col3 DESC;

SELECT dim4_col4, COUNT(DISTINCT orders) FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table2 f      JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension4 d4 ON (f.dim4_pk_1 = d4.dim4_pk_col1 AND f.dim4_pk_2 = d4.dim4_col4 AND d4.dim4_col4 = 'Client_01')      RIGHT JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension5 d5 ON (f.dim5_pk_1 = d5.dim5_pk_col1 AND f.dim5_pk_2 = d5.dim5_pk_col2 AND f.dim5_pk_3 = d5.dim5_pk_col3) GROUP BY dim4_col4;

SELECT d1.dim1_col4, SUM(f.orders), SUM(f2.agg_sales) FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table1 f      LEFT JOIN (SELECT d1.dim1_pk, SUM(sales) AS agg_sales                 FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table2 f,                      nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1                 WHERE                       f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk                 GROUP BY d1.dim1_pk) f2       ON (f.dim1_pk = f2.dim1_pk)       JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1 ON (f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk) GROUP BY d1.dim1_col4;

WITH f2 AS (SELECT d1.dim1_pk, SUM(sales) AS agg_sales                 FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table2 f,                      nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1                 WHERE                       f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk                 GROUP BY d1.dim1_pk) SELECT d1.dim1_col4, SUM(f.orders) AS sum_orders, SUM(f2.agg_sales) AS sum_sales FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table1 f      LEFT JOIN f2 ON (f.dim1_pk = f2.dim1_pk)       JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1 ON (f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk) GROUP BY d1.dim1_col4;

SELECT d1.dim1_col4, SUM(f.orders) AS sum_orders, SUM(f2.agg_sales) AS sum_sales    FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table1 f    LEFT JOIN ( SELECT d1.dim1_pk, SUM(f.sales) AS agg_sales            FROM nz_rule_test.fact_table2 f, nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1           WHERE f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk           GROUP BY d1.dim1_pk) f2 ON f.dim1_pk = f2.dim1_pk    JOIN nz_rule_test.dimension1 d1 ON f.dim1_pk = d1.dim1_pk   GROUP BY d1.dim1_col4;
